; GT4Amiga user-startup script
; Add this to s/user-startup on the Workbench disk (DH0:).
; It mounts the GT4A: shared drive and starts the program watcher.

; Mount the shared directory (FS-UAE maps it as hard drive 1)
Assign GT4A: DH1:

; Start the watcher in background (detached)
Run >NIL: GT4A:s/gt4amiga-watcher
